<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-02T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-02T00:00:00-05:00" n="465" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d465">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Presidents Special Assistant</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_HHL1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hopkins</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the Soviet
                                    Foreign Commissar</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_MVM1" type="to"><hi rend="italic">Molotov</hi></persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d465fn1">Sent to the White House Map Room, via military
                                    channels, and forwarded by the Map Room to the Embassy at
                                    Moscow, via Navy channels.</note></head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Cairo</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-02">2 December 1943</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>I did so much enjoy our conferences together<note n="2" xml:id="d465fn2">At Tehran.</note> and only hope that they may
                                be continued. I am sure that the meeting between Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1">Stalin</persName> and the President has done
                                infinite good in bringing our two countries closer together in War
                                and in Peace. I do hope you have reached home safely. With my
                                warmest regards.</p>
                            <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_HHL1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Harry
                                            Hopkins</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>